# v5-password-string is a deprecated resource type kept for backward
# compatibility only ‚Äî the server policy `isNotV5PasswordStringType` rejects
# all new creations of this type. This scenario locks in that policy: if the
# server ever starts allowing v5-password-string creation, this test will
# fail and prompt a review.

! pb create resource --type v5-password-string --name test-password-string --password simple-secret-string --json
stderr 'Could not validate resource data'
